{"tid":2493123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【學者風骨】港大法律教授 國安法陰霾下堅持 教學生 自決與反抗權，並向五毛下戰書","createTime":"2021-04-17T15:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T23:35:28.000Z","uid":138409,"like":118,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"ed65c30c2cd5674d22cadd8a7355d8d04325b391","tid":2493123,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/david.stephen.law/posts/10157630725181402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdavid.stephen.law%2Fposts%2F10157630725181402&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=4cc57b13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/david.stephen.law/posts/10157630725181402</a><br />\n<br />\n原文英文，全文翻譯如下：<br />\n<br />\n// 提醒：如果你給我的港大工作郵箱發些什麼東西，就當中國政府已經看了吧。最近一次有人從香港以外的地方登錄我的港大賬號，是在本週早些時候，當天我講授 「分裂、自決和反抗權」這一課堂單元。 (<span class=\"gold\">我不僅沒有因應「國安法」自我審查，還針對「國安法」在課程中*加了*這個課題</span>，讓學生選擇是否納入爲選修課。學生以壓倒性的優勢投票決定納入，票數超過了其他十幾個選項。所以我們就這樣做了）。<br />\n<br />\n這是巧合嗎？也許CCP國安認為它用這樣一種粗暴得令我知曉的方式黑掉我的賬戶，是在向我傳遞訊息。假若如是，我受寵若驚。但中共監控的前景對我來說不是新聞，我也沒有什麼好隱瞞的。任何人有什麼話要對我說，都可以在Facebook上公開發布&mdash;&mdash;就像我一樣。我無意隱瞞自己的觀點，正因為我知道中共國安一直在監視&mdash;&mdash;也因為我從經驗中知道，中共和它的同路人不可能贏得任何實際的是非曲直爭論。像任何專制政權一樣，中共必須依賴鎮壓、恐嚇、宣傳、恐懼，以及（在中國越來越）迎合民族主義。<br />\n<br />\n所以現在正在讀這篇文章的人，不管你是誰&mdash;&mdash;來吧，我向你挑戰，就在這裡進行一場辯論。<span class=\"gold\">在香港，所有心水清的人都知道，親中派如不採取恐嚇、鎮壓和赤裸裸的不誠實手段，是不可能獲勝的。</span>但在這裡，在我的Facebook頁面上？評論是開放的。而且只有你的言論才是重要的。<span class=\"gold\">站在你那邊的是一個未經同意就進行統治的警察國家。而我這邊：事實，邏輯，道德。</span>//"},{"pid":"68f9b8d4499a26f639147b65952bc02402574882","tid":2493123,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7328f0c59cf3b13c5150a63313f89ae0f8eae477","tid":2493123,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教授"},{"pid":"c4fe7dcb3eca08fa3b266ead4a44e6f1d6345d8f","tid":2493123,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c97fc65626ed7cc0c0415a49a776645aed9c6a0","tid":2493123,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f9bc8397c3b39d2fee6c0a257776f6200a0122f5","tid":2493123,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"deccb77e68658fafc983bcaa8505ed13cc3af79c","tid":2493123,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd4606b8211ba8555f2a90ca8439d5fe05bad3b","tid":2493123,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24184fe503fc7ebe840bf71687dc2ee9d944f130","tid":2493123,"uid":35465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aca2888589d9fdd6246da200fd65f0cd100662e","tid":2493123,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki